# textdomain: mcl_redstone_torch
Redstone Torch (off)=Harrigorri lastargia (itzalita)
A redstone torch is a redstone component which can be used to invert a redstone signal. It supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power, except for the block it is attached to. A redstone torch is normally lit, but it can also be turned off by powering the block it is attached to. While unlit, a redstone torch does not power anything.=Harrigorri lastargi bat harrigorri seinale bat alderantzikatzeko erabil daitekeen harrigorri osagai bat da. Inguruko blokeei harrigorri energia ematen die, lotuta dagoen blokeari izan ezik. Harrigorri lastargi bat piztuta egon ohi da, baina konektatuta dagoen blokea elikatuz ere itzal daiteke. Itzalita dagoen bitartean, harrigorri lastargi batek ez du ezer elikatzen.
Redstone torches can be placed at the side and on the top of full solid opaque blocks.=Harrigorri lastargiak alde batean jar daitezke, eta goiko aldean, berriz, bloke opako solido osoak.
Redstone Torch=Harrigorri lastargia
Block of Redstone=Redstone blokea
Provides redstone power=Redstone seinalea igortzen du
A block of redstone permanently supplies redstone power to its surrounding blocks.=Redstone bloke batek redstone energia ematen die etengabe inguruko blokeei.
